  <brief_title>The Effect of Elemental Diet on Gastric Emptying</brief_title>
  <acronym>Elental</acronym>
  <official_title>The Comparative Study of Elemental Diet and Regular Liquid Diet on Gastric Emptying in Patients With Percutaneous Endoscopic Gastrostomy</official_title>
